---
import DemoLayout from '../../../layouts/DemoLayout.astro';
---

<DemoLayout
  title="Cloudflare Workers"
  description="Build, deploy, and scale apps across Cloudflare's global network with Workers - a serverless platform with no infrastructure to manage."
  category="Developer Platform"
  labels={["Workers", "Serverless", "Edge Computing", "Compute"]}
  lastUpdated="November 2025"
>

  <!-- Overview Card -->
  <section class="card" aria-labelledby="overview-heading">
    <h2 id="overview-heading">Overview</h2>
    <p>
      Cloudflare Workers is a serverless platform for building, deploying, and scaling applications across
      Cloudflare's global network with a single command — no infrastructure to manage, no complex configuration.
    </p>

    <h3 class="subsection-heading">What You Get</h3>
    <ul class="feature-list">
      <li>Fast performance with high reliability on Cloudflare's global network</li>
      <li>Support for JavaScript, TypeScript, Python, Rust, and more</li>
      <li>Integration with popular frameworks like React, Next.js, Astro, and Vue</li>
      <li>Free tier with flexible pricing that scales with your needs</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="subsection-heading">Common Use Cases</h3>
    <ul class="feature-list">
      <li>
        Full-stack applications with static assets and APIs ({' '}
        <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/workers/runtime-apis/bindings/" target="_blank" rel="external noopener noreferrer">Bindings</a>)
      </li>
      <li>Serverless AI inference with Workers AI</li>
      <li>Background jobs and scheduled tasks</li>
      <li>Real-time collaboration and chat applications</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="subsection-heading">
      <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/workers/platform/storage-options/" target="_blank" rel="external noopener noreferrer">
        Storage &amp; Data Options
      </a>
    </h3>
    <p>Integrate seamlessly with Cloudflare's data products:</p>
    <ul class="feature-list">
      <li><strong>KV:</strong> Low-latency key-value storage for configuration and session data</li>
      <li><strong>D1:</strong> Serverless SQL database for structured data</li>
      <li><strong>R2:</strong> Object storage with zero egress fees</li>
      <li><strong>Durable Objects:</strong> Stateful coordination with strong consistency</li>
      <li><strong>Queues:</strong> Message queuing for reliable background processing</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- Demos Grid -->
  <section aria-labelledby="demos-heading">
    <h2 id="demos-heading">Serverless Demos</h2>
    <div class="demos-grid">
      <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/workers/playground/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external" class="demo-link">
        Workers Playground
      </a>
      <a href="https://petstore.automatic-demo.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external" class="demo-link">
        Petstore API Demo
      </a>
      <a href="https://graphql.automatic-demo.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external" class="demo-link">
        GraphQL API Demo
      </a>
      <a href="https://github.com/DavidJKTofan/cf-workers-httpbin" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external" class="demo-link">
        HTTPBin Service
      </a>
      <a href="https://davidtofan.com/articles/cloudflare-logpush/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external" class="demo-link">
        Logpush Guide
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="btn-row mt-2">
      <a
        href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/workers/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer external"
        class="btn btn-outline"
      >
        View Documentation
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</DemoLayout>

<style>
  /* ===== Section spacing ===== */
  section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  section > h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 3vw, 1.45rem);
    color: var(--secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
  }

  /* ===== Card ===== */
  .card {
    background-color: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .card h2 {
    border-bottom-color: var(--border);
  }

  .card p, section > p {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ===== Subsection heading ===== */
  .subsection-heading {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--secondary);
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem;
  }

  /* ===== Feature list ===== */
  .feature-list {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0.75rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ===== Demos Grid ===== */
  .demos-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .demo-link {
    display: block;
    padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
    background-color: var(--secondary);
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: center;
    transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
    border-bottom: none !important;
  }

  .demo-link:hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    color: white;
    border-bottom: none !important;
  }

  /* ===== Button Row ===== */
  .btn-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
    border-bottom: none !important;
  }

  .btn:hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    border-bottom: none !important;
  }

  .btn-outline {
    background-color: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .btn-outline:hover {
    background-color: var(--hover);
  }

  /* ===== Utility ===== */
  .mt-2 { margin-top: 1.5rem; }
</style>
